VVith sundry other collections, annexed by the translator for the more cleere and exact satisfaction of the reader. With a short chronicle in the end, of the liues and raignes of the Venetian dukes, from the very beginninges of their citie De magistribus et republica Venetorum. English Contarini, Gasparo, 1483-1542. Lewkenor, Lewis, Sir, d. 1626.

Imprinted by Iohn Windet for Edmund Mattes, and are to be sold at his shop, at the signe of the Hand and Plow in Fleetstreet, London : 1599.
